videos.description: Isaac Yiadom picks off Josh Jackson and returns it 9 yards to Virginia Tech's 25-yard line.
videos.headline: BC forces first turnover of the game

videos.description: Travon McMillian breaks free for a 23-yard touchdown run to give the Hokies a 17-3 lead.
videos.headline: Virginia State's McMillian runs for 23-yard TD

videos.description: Anthony Brown throws a 32-yard pass to Kobay White for a first down at Virginia Tech's 31 yard line.
videos.headline: BC gets into Virginia Tech territory with big play

videos.description: Josh Jackson throws a strike to Sean Savoy for a 53-yard touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Hokies strike first with 53-yard TD

videos.description: Steve Addazio says his team is doing some good things on offense and defense, but they've missed a few opportunities in the first half.
videos.headline: BC coach Steve Addazio discuses missed opportunities in the first half

videos.description: Josh Jackson connects with Sean Savoy for a 46-yard catch to put the Hokies in Boston College territory, leading to a field goal.
videos.headline: Virgina Tech's Savoy makes a defender miss after big catch

videos.description: Jeff Smith throws a 25-yard touchdown pass to quarterback Anthony Brown to bring the Eagles within 13.
videos.headline: Smith completes pass to QB for Eagles first TD of the game

videos.description: Hokies head coach Justin Fuente is pleased with the win, but says his team still needs to improve.
videos.headline: Fuente says Virginia Tech has to get better

videos.description: Josh Jackson gives credit to Sean Savoy and Eric Kumah for stepping up after starting receiver Cam Phillips went down with an injury.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech QB Josh Jackson praises recievers

videos.description: Ahmad Brooks says Boston College had a lot of missed opportunities and dropped passes in loss to Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Ahmad Brooks and Mike Corey recap No.16 Virginia Tech's 23-10 win over Boston College
